CEZ Will Need to Borrow to Expand Temelin Plant, Lidove Reports

-- B y   P e t e r   L a c a
-- 
2011-09-20T06:02:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/cez-will-need-to-borrow-to-expand-temelin-plant-lidove-reports.html
CEZ AS (CEZ) , the largest Czech power
producer, will need to borrow to finance the expansion of its
Temelin nuclear power plant,  Lidove Noviny  reported, citing
Finance Minister Miroslav Kalousek.  CEZ, which is controlled by the state, is currently in the
process of choosing contractors for two new reactors at the
Temelin plant.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Peter Laca in Prague at 
 placa@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Balazs Penz at 
 bpenz@bloomberg.net  